  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To Study the Efficacy of Aurosling as a suspension material in Frontalis suspension surgery
      in ptosis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Silicon rod is an effective and safe material used in frontalis suspension in treating ptosis
      with poor levator function.The elasticity and ease of adjustment of silicon rod are ideal
      characteristics for suspension material used to treat severe ptosis in patients with poor
      bells phenomenon. In the present study , we attend to study the efficacy of aurosling silicon
      material as a suspension material for frontalis sling surgery
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
